title: Hardgainer Project X - New Guide For Muscle Building
description:
Hardgainer Project X is a brand new program that will revolutionize skinny and underweight people's lives. 

If your a skinny man then Hardgainer Project X will kick your genetic limitations out of the ball park and you will gain weight and muscle super fast.

Hardgainer Project X was created by fitness trainer Jeff Anderson who carried out an experiment using 6 "human skinny lab rats" and put them through a 12 week training geared up especially for hardgainers and the results at the end of the 12 week period were unbelievable!
